            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 08:15:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價收跌逾4%　美國對伊朗採取軍事行動擔憂緩和",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原油期貨價格急跌逾4%收市，結束5個交易日升勢。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil_source-ap_-4.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil_source-ap_-4.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油收報每桶59.19美元，下跌2.83美元，跌幅4.56%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶63.76美元，下跌2.76美元，跌幅4.15%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國總統特朗普表示，伊朗對示威的鎮壓有所緩和，市場減低美國或對伊朗採取軍事行動和石油供應中斷的擔憂。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15586427-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be4%e3%80%80%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e5%b0%8d%e4%bc%8a%e6%9c%97%e6%8e%a1%e5%8f%96%e8%bb%8d%e4%ba%8b%e8%a1%8c%e5%8b%95%e6%93%94%e6%86%82%e7%b7%a9%e5%92%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil_source-ap_-1-1-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 08:10:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價急挫逾4%　美國介入伊朗局勢可能性或減",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15586099&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際油價急挫逾4%，市場對美國介入伊朗局勢的憂慮降溫。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油報每桶59.12美元，跌2.77美元，跌幅4.47%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油較早時報每桶63.63美元，跌2.89美元，跌幅4.35%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國總統特朗普較早時表示，目前沒有計劃對伊朗展開大規模行動。</p>\n</div>",
